
Purchase Ticket:
1.
POST /api/train/purchase
{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}
2. View Receipt 
GET /api/train/receipt?email=john.doe@example.com
3.View Users by Section 
GET /api/train/users?section=A
4. Remove User from Train
DELETE /api/train/remove?email=john.doe@example.com
5. Modify User's Seat
PUT /api/train/modify?email=m.scott@example.com&newSection=B